                    "body": "Do you already have code for this? then please contribute it :-)\r\n\r\nDoes this bug appear on PHPs SoapClient also? If yes, please report a bug on php.net",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=beberlei",
                        "name": "beberlei",
